  "prompt": "What is the easiest way to get my transcript from Mahatma Gandhi University, Kottayam?",
  "response": "Getting your transcript from Mahatma Gandhi University (MGU), Kottayam, is a straightforward process. Here\u2019s the easiest way to do it:\n\n### Step-by-Step Guide:\n1. **Visit the MGU Official Website**  \n   Go to [Mahatma Gandhi University's official website](https://www.mgu.ac.in/).\n\n2. **Navigate to the Examination Section**  \n   Look for the \"Examination\" or \"Student Services\" tab on the website. This section typically provides details related to transcripts, mark sheets, and other academic documents.\n\n3. **Find the Transcript Application Form**  \n   Search for the transcript application form or the procedure for requesting transcripts. The form is often available for download in the \"Examination\" or \"Forms\" section.\n\n4. **Fill Out the Application Form**  \n   Complete the form with your personal details, such as your name, registration number, course details, and any other required information.\n\n5. **Attach Required Documents**  \n   Gather the necessary documents, which may include:\n   - Copy of your degree certificate\n   - Mark sheets\n   - Identity proof\n   - Passport-sized photograph\n   - Demand draft (if payment is required)\n\n6. **Pay the Transcript Fee**  \n   Check the fee details on the website. Payment is typically made via demand draft or online payment. Make sure to follow the instructions provided.\n\n7. **Submit the Application**  \n   Submit the completed application form along with the required documents and payment receipt to the university's Examination Section. You can do this:\n   - **In Person:** Visit the university campus and submit the application at the designated office.\n   - **By Post:** Send the application via registered mail to the university's address.  \n   **Address:**  \n   The Controller of Examinations,  \n   Mahatma Gandhi University,  \n   Priyadarsini Hills, Kottayam - 686560,  \n   Kerala, India.\n\n8. **Track Your Application**  \n   After submission, you can track the status of your transcript application through the university's website or by contacting the Examination Section.\n\n9. **Receive Your Transcript**  \n   Once processed, the transcript will be sent to your mailing address or can be collected in person, depending on the option you chose.\n\n### Additional Tips:\n- **Email Inquiry**: If you have any doubts, you can email the Examination Section at `exam@mgu.ac.in` for clarification.\n- **Online Portal**: Check if the university has an online portal for transcript requests, as this can simplify the process.\n- **Processing Time**: Allow sufficient time for processing, as it may take a few weeks depending on the university\u2019s workload.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to obtain your transcript from Mahatma Gandhi University, Kottayam, without much hassle.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
